videos.description: Baylor's Johnathan Motley gets a kind bounce on his turnaround jumper and the foul.
videos.headline: Motley and-1 jumper rattles home

videos.description: Deonte Burton meets Jo Lual-Acuil at the rim with the swat but Ishmail Wainright gets the layup.
videos.headline: Burton rejects Acuil with a vicious block

videos.description: Deonte Burton rejects another Baylor attempt to go inside.
videos.headline: Burton swats shot into the bleachers

videos.description: Johnathan Motley grabs the offensive rebound before throwing down a huge dunk.
videos.headline: Motley rocks the rim with a ferocious slam

videos.description: After finding himself open under the rim, Solomon Young throws down the dunk.
videos.headline: Young rattles the rim with a big two-handed dunk

videos.description: Johnathan Motley takes advantage of his man turning his back on him and throws down a big dunk.
videos.headline: Motley rocks the rim with a big dunk

videos.description: Jo Lual-Acuil Jr. reaches over four Cyclones' players and throws down the dunk.
videos.headline: Acuil Jr. grabs the rebound over four Cyclones and dunks it down

videos.description: Solomon Young rejects a shot which leads to Donovan Jackson burying a 3-pointer from the wing.
videos.headline: Young blocks leads to transition three for Jackson

videos.description: King McClure knocks down a 3-pointer late in the game. Can the Cyclones hang on?
videos.headline: McClure buries a big 3-pointer

videos.description: No. 9 Baylor goes down 72-69 as surging Cyclones pick up fifth straight win.
videos.headline: Deonte Burton powers Cyclones to fifth straight win
